<div class="block"><img src="http://static.indianexpress.com/m-images/Thu Jan 12 2012, 16:21 hrs/M_Id_261168_internet_usage.jpg" alt="Internet usage"  class="story" width="170" title="Internet craving can be as bad as drug usage. (Reuters)"><br />
<!--<div class="box_facebookNew"><span></span><iframe scrolling="no" frameborder="0" src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/likebox.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Findianexpress&amp;width=170 &amp;colorscheme=light&amp;connections=0&amp;stream=false&amp;header=true&amp;height=72" style="border: medium none; background:#ebe9ea; overflow: hidden; width: 170px; height: 72px;" allowtransparency="true"></iframe> </div>-->

<iframe scrolling="n"  height='1000' width='180' frameborder="0" src="http://www.indianexpress.com/moreFromIE.php" ></iframe>

</div>
